  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to study the response of macrophages, isolated from patients
      with ulcerative colitis (Crohn's disease) or Crohn's disease (CD), to 6 candidate
      enterogenous and their derivatives, depending on the genotype for associated polymorphisms.
      to the development of IBD
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
